<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.2.6">
<l>kiṟpaṉ killē ṉeṉṟilaṉ muṉanāḷā</l>
<l>laṟpacā raṅka ḷavaicuvait takaṉṟoḻintēṉ</l>
<l>paṟpal lāyira muyirceyta paramāniṉ</l>
<l>ṉaṟpoṉcō tittā ṇaṇukuva teññāṉṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I did not say “I can, I cannot”. I ended up parting after</l>
<l>tasting those: trifling saps through the former days.</l>
<l>O Highest on who made many many thousand lives,</l>
<l>at which time will there be my reaching you good golden-light feet?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
